<div class="well">
    Key2Gym is a free software for running and maintaining gyms and other 
    membership-based clubs or enterprises. This application has been written 
    with the ideas of simplicity and powerful functionality in mind.
    This documentation describes the installation, configuring and administration of the 
    Key2Gym application.
</div>

<div class="well">
    The application consists of 3 tiers: the database tier, the business tier,
    and the client tier. This documentation is therefore separated
    into 3 parts. Each part is dedicated to installation, configuration and maintaining
    of one of the tiers.
</div>

